      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide your<strong> vegan burger patty[ies]</strong> and shape them into 3 meat-free meatballs per person (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>meatballs </strong>to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side or until beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
